<DOCNO> LA080389-0013 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 89971 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 3, 1989, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part 2; Page 7; Column 1; Op-Ed Desk 
</P>
