<HEADLINE>
<P>
A WILD RIDE WINS JUNIOR MISS STAKES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A Wild Ride overtook 7-10 favorite Dominant Dancer in the late going Wednesday 
to win the $84,675 Junior Miss Stakes by three-quarters of a length before a 
crowd of 14,362 at Del Mar. 
</P>
<P>
A Wild Ride, ridden by Chris McCarron and carrying 115 pounds, covered six 
furlongs in 1:09 4/5 and paid $9.80, $3.60 and $3.20.. 
</P>
<P>
Dominant Dancer finished six lengths in front of Tanya's Tuition and returned 
$2.60 and $2.40. Tanya's Tuition, a 48-1 shot paid $7.60 to show. 
</P>
</TEXT>
