COMMISSION; SPORTS FRANCHISES; DAVIS, AL; IRWINDALE (CA) -- CONTRACTS; OAKLAND 
(CA) -- CONTRACTS; BUILDING RESTORATIONS; LOS ANGELES -- CONTRACTS; STADIUMS 
</P>
