EXHIBITION GAMES; FOOTBALL PLAYERS; AMERICAN BOWL (FOOTBALL GAME); JAPAN -- 
CULTURE; AMERICANS -- JAPAN; RACIAL DISCRIMINATION; CULTURE SHOCK 
</P>
