<TEXT>
<P>
Former tennis star Bjorn Borg has "personally promised" to meet the debts of 
his fashion company, the president of the firm, Stig Sjoblom, said in a 
statement on behalf of the Bjorn Borg Design Group. 
</P>
<P>
Borg, 33, announced last week that he will close the Scandinavian division of 
the clothing empire. 
