<P>
Photo, Gretchen Magers hasn't won a tournament in 1989, but it still has been a 
good year so far. ROBERT FAABORG / For The Times* GARRISON SURVIVESAs usual, 
Terry Phelps plays Zina Garrison tough before losing. Story, Page 11A. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
