<P>
Photo, A typical Sunday scene at the Orange Coast College gym, where table 
tennis club members sharpen their skills on the 20 tables set up on the floor. 
; Photo, Mas Hashimoto makes the trip from Pacoima to play at OCC. JOHN FUNG / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
