<P>
SUITS; LEE &amp; ASSOCIATES; REAL ESTATE BROKERS; REAL ESTATE INDUSTRY -- 
ORANGE COUNTY; FINANCES; COLDWELL BANKER COMMERCIAL REAL ESTATE SERVICES 
</P>
